	<h2>What is Daily Budget Life?</h2>
	<p>Daily Budget Life is a personal finance blog for people who want straightforward money advice. No financial jargon. No get-rich-quick schemes. Just practical, actionable tips for budgeting, saving, and building wealth over time.</p>
	
	<h2>What We Write About</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Budgeting</strong> — Simple systems that actually work in real life.</li>
		<li><strong>Saving Money</strong> — Practical ways to spend less without feeling deprived.</li>
		<li><strong>Apps & Tools</strong> — Honest reviews of budgeting and finance apps.</li>
		<li><strong>Investing Basics</strong> — Getting started without needing a finance degree.</li>
		<li><strong>Side Hustles</strong> — Realistic ways to earn extra income.</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
	<p>Money advice should be free and accessible. We don't sell courses. We don't push expensive financial products. We write what we'd tell a friend who asked for help with their finances.</p>
</Layout>
